name: Ace Trainer BW (Pokemon Black and White)
description:
Female ace trainer from pokemon black and white

Use acebw as trigger word.

You may want to add "Orange vest", "long sleeves", "blue skirt", "pantyhose", "drill_hair" to your Prompt
use between 0.7 - 1.0 weight

Trained on Nai

All images were generated using yabalMix (https://civitai.com/models/28648/yabalmix) with xformers on and using kl-f8-anime2 vae.

images were generated at 512x768 and upscaled using highres fix by 1.95 and using 4x_foolhardy_Remacri upscaler
